### 로그인 (TL 계정 — 1차 평가용)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeEmail": "tl@company.com",
  "password": "password123!"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

###

### 1차 평가 임시저장 — 성공
POST http://localhost:8081/api/team-leader/evaluations/1/draft
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "evaluationPeriodId": 1,
  "evalItems": "{\"TECHNICAL_COMPETENCE\": 80, \"SAFETY_COMPLIANCE\": 75}",
  "evalComment": "이번 분기 설비 대응 역량이 크게 향상되었습니다.",
  "inputMethod": "TEXT"
}

###

### 1차 평가 임시저장 — 실패 (inputMethod 누락, 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/team-leader/evaluations/1/draft
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "evaluationPeriodId": 1,
  "evalItems": null,
  "evalComment": null,
  "inputMethod": null
}

###

### 1차 평가 제출 — 성공 (grade 자동 산출)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/team-leader/evaluations/1/submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "evaluationPeriodId": 1,
  "evalItems": "{\"TECHNICAL_COMPETENCE\": 90, \"SAFETY_COMPLIANCE\": 85}",
  "evalComment": "이번 분기 설비 대응 역량이 크게 향상되었으며 안전 수칙도 철저히 준수하였습니다.",
  "inputMethod": "TEXT",
  "score": 92.0
}

###

### 1차 평가 제출 — 실패 (코멘트 20자 미만, 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/team-leader/evaluations/1/submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "evaluationPeriodId": 1,
  "evalItems": null,
  "evalComment": "짧은 코멘트",
  "inputMethod": "TEXT",
  "score": 85.0
}

###

### 1차 평가 제출 — 실패 (score 범위 초과, 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/team-leader/evaluations/1/submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "evaluationPeriodId": 1,
  "evalItems": null,
  "evalComment": "이번 분기 설비 대응 역량이 크게 향상되었습니다.",
  "inputMethod": "TEXT",
  "score": 110.0
}
